under which the standard branes of $n = 0,1$ are mapped to the exotic branes of $n = 4,3$ and vice versa, and the solitonic branes of $n = 2$ are mapped to other solitonic branes \cite{Bergshoeff:2011se, Sakatani:2014hba}.
